headline: Erie Indemnity to host first quarter 2025 pre-recorded conference call and webcast
summary: Erie Indemnity Company (NASDAQ: ERIE) will host a pre-recorded audio webcast with the financial community providing financial results for the first quarter on Friday, Apr 25th, at 10 a.m. Eastern Time. Erie Indemnity will issue a press release reporting its results after the close of the market on Thursday, Apr 24th.
